  "summary": "Malicious code in sam-package (npm)",
  "details": "The postinstall script silently fires an HTTPS GET to webhooksite[.]net/206fe563-3cfb-42fc-b589-b8b748b4c640 on every installation, acting as a beacon that transmits the installer's IP address, user-agent, and request metadata to a remote collector. This behaviour is unrelated to the advertised greeting-function module and is not disclosed in the package documentation.",
